These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, sprite, water
City: marseilles, liverpool, rome, edinburgh
1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
3. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
5. the person traveling to marseilles is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | sprite |
| City   | rome | edinburgh      | marseilles | liverpool |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, canasta, domino
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the person playing billiard is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game   | domino | canasta | billiard   | scrabble |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, electronic
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, quad-bike, train
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
5. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
6. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre        | hip-hop | gospel | rock     | electronic |
| Transport   | car  | train   | quad-bike | bus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: fish, rat, lizard, pony
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the rat##2
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
5. the owner of the pony is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Pet   | pony   | lizard     | rat    | fish       |

