.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
House: futuristic, townhouse, modern, victorian
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the modern house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| House   | townhouse  | victorian | futuristic | modern |

