2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the turkish is between the person drinking cola and the thai##2
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Beverage           | water | sprite | cola | fanta |
| Nationality   | thai        | turkish     | japanese       | russian   |

