.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
City: hamburg, berlin, marseilles, san-francisco
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, mechanic, scientist
1. the librarian is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| City   | berlin     | san-francisco | marseilles     | hamburg   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

