.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, bolivar, cain
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
5. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5
6. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| Cigar       | ritmeester       | bolivar   | cain | swisher |

