.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, daisy, balloon-flower, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, water-polo
1. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | begonia | daisy   | balloon-flower | bellflower     |
| Sport   | parkour     | badminton | soccer  | water-polo |

