.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, october, january, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| Birthday         | january  | march | april | october |

