4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, fish, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the horse is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing | dancing | camping |
| Pet   | hedgehog     | guinea-pig  | horse  | fish    |

