The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, tram
1. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
2. the person traveling to liverpool is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| City   | new-york     | boston | marseilles | liverpool |
| Transport     | helicopter | bike    | taxi    | tram |

