.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend, vegafina, cain
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
3. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the blend-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Cigar   | vegafina | cain  | bongani | blend        |

