.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, strawberry, watermelon
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, chestnut, apricot, purple
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the right of the person who likes chestnut##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating watermelon and the person who likes aquamarine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes     | watermelon | asparagus | strawberry |
| Color   | apricot | purple | chestnut      | aquamarine        |

 